  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had in our-- in our movement in Krakow, they were soliciting people, and they were from the movement to come over to Krakow to the headquarters, and they supplied them with Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, Gusta Davidson and Shimich Draenger were specialists in making those counterfeit-- the Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were so good that sometimes the people did not recognize that it wasn't their [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] signature.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The forms were stolen from the German office by people that were working there, Jewish people that were working there as cleaning crews, and they stole-- from our group-- and they stole those papers and supplied them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they made the Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Minka Liebeskind, when she came, she brought those papers to certain people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to have good looks and a good Polish [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] pronunciation in order to make use of those papers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you could have all the courage, but if you had black hair and black eyes and-- and features that were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] here they would look like Italians and like Spanish, like French people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you had those looks in Poland, since those other nationalities didn't live there, you were unmistakably a Jew, and you took your life in your hand whether you had Aryan papers or not.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And specifically, if you were a young man, besides the bad looks, if they could disrobe you and see that you were circumcised, you were in real trouble.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and there were a lot of people, I'm sorry to say, Polish people, instead of realizing that the Germans were our common enemy, they still denounced the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
